import React from 'react' import uuid from 'react-uuid'; import { useEffect } from 'react'; function Viewall(props) { useEffect(() => ( window.scrollTo(0, 0))) let data = Array.from(props.latest); return (
    { data.map((n) =>
    {n.date}

    {n.heading}

    ~{n.details}

    ) }
) } export default Viewall
